    "description": "<p>Supermath Learning Centre specialize in Primary School Math, Secondary Math, IP Math, and AEIS Cambridge Math offering expert math tutoring in a small class-size setting. Our exclusive math curriculum is MOE-aligned which is highly sought after by parents. The in-house Math worksheets are tailored to your child's progress, ensuring personalized effective learning. We aim to create a vibrant learning support group in Singapore, making mathematics fun and engaging with all students. Join us and experience the best Singapore Math tuition.</p>",
